This package vendors and adapts code from:

  jlens-gguf — https://github.com/igorbarshteyn/jlens-gguf
  Copyright 2026, licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

Adapted files: lens.py, readout.py, model_reader.py, fitting.py (verbatim
with intra-package import paths updated and an MTP/NextN-aware readable-layer
count added), native_client.py (ported from `requests` to `httpx`).

The underlying method is the Jacobian lens from Anthropic's "Verbalizable
Representations Form a Global Workspace in Language Models"
(https://transformer-circuits.pub/2026/workspace) and the reference
implementation at https://github.com/anthropics/jacobian-lens (Apache-2.0).

